    "The HuatuoGPT-sft-data-v1 dataset is a Chinese medical instruction dataset designed for the instruction fine-tuning phase of the HuatuoGPT model.",
    "The dataset combines refined data generated by the model and authentic dialogue data provided by real doctors, totaling 226K instructions.",
    "• Huatuo-26M (Li et al, 2023h).",
    "The Huatuo-26M dataset is a Chinese medical Q&A dataset comprising 26M high-quality medical Q&A pairs.",
    "The medical topics covered include diseases, symptoms, treatment methods, drug information, and more."
